  "title": "HYDRAULIC TECHNICIAN",
  "description": "<p>Hydraulic Technician</p><p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><p>· Able to carry out a fitter’s job with a number of years of hands-on experiences </p><p>· Knowledge of hydraulic pumps, hydraulic cylinders, motors, various directional flow and pressure control components</p><p>· Knowledge and experience to overhaul the hydraulic pumps, motors and cylinders are crucial </p><p>· Able to work in workshop and shipyards and onboard vessels.</p><p>· Able to read hydraulic circuit diagrams is useful</p><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS               </strong></p><p>· Singaporean or PR</p><p>· NITEC in Mechanical Engineering or relevant trade certificates</p><p>· Strong Team Player</p><p>· Possess good attitude</p><p><strong>OTHERS</strong></p><p>· 13 month bonus</p><p>· Medical Benefits</p><p>· Lunch Provided</p><p>· Near Pioneer MRT, West</p><p>· 5.5 days work Week (Excluding public holidays)</p><p>· Able to commence work immediately/ one month notice</p><p>· Singaporeans / PR only</p><p>· Communicating in English is essential and can speak other languages will be useful</p>",
